          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Probably one of the worst schools if you have this school in your bucket list for admitting your ward. About me, I am a 2021 aluminus and I have to put this forward that this school does not care about you unless you are providing them with surplus cash other than the fees without giving any white paper regards to the payments.\nThe teachers especially the male PE teachers absolutely gang up on students and do not refrain from using force even for petty issues. All these events make the environment in school extremely unhealthy for younger students and toddlers.\n\nMediocre students are pushed back and favoritism always has the final word in this school. This happens every single day, leading to insecurity and lack of opportunities among vast majority of students.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
