          "datePublished": "2022-12-06",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "WARNING!!\nIf you care for the future of your kids don't send them to Ryan International School.\n1).This school don't care for your children's education. All they care about is publicity and their money grabbing scemes are sickening.\n2).They don't teach children in their classes but instead expect the parents to do it at home.  They give lots of assignments which the students have no clue on how to deal with it. In sort those assignments are for parents to do.\n3).The students will have to contribute money for all kinds of activities which are charged way over the required expenditure. The school administration is a joke.\nThey don't even deserve a 1/5* rating. This school need to be shutdown by the government.",
          "publisher": {
